  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: "When you would play this card, you can also place cards
    from your trash in digivolution cards for a DigiXros.\n[On Play] [When Digivolving]
    You may play 1 purple level 4 or lower Digimon card or 1 level 4 or lower Digimon
    card with the [Xros Heart]\_trait from your trash without paying the cost. If
    DigiXrosing, add 1 to the number of cards you play with this effect.\n[All Turns]
    All of your Digimon with the [Xros Heart]\_trait or with \uFF1CRetaliation\uFF1E
    gain \uFF1CRush\uFF1Eand \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E.\n\n[DigiXros\_-3] 1 Digimon card
    with [Xros Heart]\_trait"
